snippet.title: The Disobedient Dietician, a conversation with Amber Gourley
snippet.description:
Episode 3 of Conscious LIfe Space's Conversations a Podcast
#podcast #nutrition #health
Thank you for watching this conversational interview with Amber Gourley, The Disobedient Dietician
-----
Read more about Amber in the show notes here: 

https://consciouslife.guru/podcast/the-disobedient-dietician-a-conversation-with-amber-gourley/

Join her FB group here:

Amy Adams, author of Gratitude Shmatitude: Don’t just think it, do it!, is the founder of The Mindful Soul Center (formerly Conscious Life Space.) The Mindful Soul Center is a publishing and media company that produces The Mindful Soul Center magazine The Mindful Soul Center podcast.  She is a creative entrepreneur, and hosts The Mindful Soul Center, a talk show distributed as a podcast. The show connects with a variety of people  - practitioners and experts in wellness, meditation, yoga, and more. Guests share their expertise and what they've learned with others so we can hear stories and learn together. Be inspired, get motivated and have a listen!
